  communicate empathically. Because of the limited nature of the link, only
  general emotional content (such as fear, hunger, happiness, curiosity) can be
  communicated. Note that the low Intelligence of a low-level master’s familiar
  limits what the creature is able to communicate or understand, and even
  intelligent familiars see the world differently from humans, so
  misunderstandings are always possible.

  Because of this empathic link, the master has the same connection to an item
  or place that his familiar does. For instance, if his familiar has seen a
  room, the master can teleport into that room as if he has seen it too.";
  short description "Communicate general emotional content up to a mile away.";
